This security photo is from right around the time it happened. There is a $3,500 reward offered by her family to anyone who has information that helps identify her.

If you recognize this woman, please call 1-800-577-8477.</div><div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/vTWqaNd.png" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div>This is Barbara. She was full of life and still working up until the moment of the attack. She was a vocal coach for years, active in the Broadway scene for a long time. I grew up hearing stories about this wild and life-loving woman, but never had the opportunity to meet her...and I just got off the phone with my grandma who gave me the news before sharing more wonderful stories.

She was a great person...and I'm reaching out to folks here who may not have already seen this in the news, hoping someone might have any information. It's a longshot, but if you recognize the person please call that number. It won't do anything to change what happened...but at the very least I hope that identifying her may lead to some semblance of closure for the people who loved Barbara...and there were more than can be counted who have benefited from her friendship directly, and millions more who were brought joy by the work she did.

Anyway...thank you for taking a moment to read this.</div></div>]]></description><guid>https://imgur.com/a/P75T3cG</guid><dc:creator><![CDATA[LookingForDwightSchrute]]></dc:creator></item><item><title>Here’s a bit of Star Wars fun for your Friday!</title><link>https://imgur.com/gallery/lmlyv0W</link><description><![CDATA[<div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/73CMcPu.gif" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div></div>]]></description><guid>https://imgur.com/a/lmlyv0W</guid><dc:creator><![CDATA[ALDSS]]></dc:creator></item><item><title>Soot_sprite_o as Raven</title><link>https://imgur.com/gallery/eCoybcu</link><description><![CDATA[<div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/LGGB6yP.jpg" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div></div>]]></description><guid>https://imgur.com/a/eCoybcu</guid><dc:creator><![CDATA[Sootspriteo]]></dc:creator></item><item><title>Love is more than one world</title><link>https://imgur.com/gallery/O1kAoiL</link><description><![CDATA[<div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/H0j9a9V.jpg" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/aiOpeZW.jpg" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/9jxPX1m.jpg" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/z6NWI4J.jpg" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/Re4ifZY.jpg" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/0jmJSTr.jpg" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/U4U67rH.jpg" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/7u4Pzks.jpg" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></s